comments: Replay review of the foul called on Graham (CHA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.  While he is moving towards Morris (NYK), Graham would have missed him if Morris hadn't extended his leg to his side during his shooting motion.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and does not deliver any contact.
Robinson (NYK) makes arm to ball contact initially, then legally blocks Zeller's (CHA) driving shot attempt.
After Graham (CHA) establishes front court status, he naturally loses his dribble causing the ball to go into the backcourt.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Rozier's (CHA) path.
Rozier (CHA) makes a slight brush touch to Morris Sr.'s (NYK) front that does not affect his upward shooting motion.
Payton (NYK) makes marginal contact with Graham (CHA) as he dribbles. The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Zeller (CHA) slightly turns his lower body after he legally establishes himself in a legal picking position in Payton's (NYK) path. The contact is marginal.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact.
Ntilikina (NYK) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Robinson (NYK) legally firms up in Monk's (CHA) path and does not deliver any contact.
Randle (NYK) makes contact with Rozier's (CHA) body after he secures the rebound.
Martin (CHA) legally contests Morris Sr.'s (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Williams (CHA) and Randle (NYK) engage during the rebound, and continue to stay engaged during the possession. Neither play delivers contact or affects the others' FOM.
Ntilikina (NYK) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Washington (CHA) legally blocks Payton's (NYK) driving shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) makes incidental leg to leg contact with Payton (NYK) during the rebound.
Ntilikina (NYK) commits a take foul on Graham (CHA).
Randle (NYK) briefly grasps Washington's (CHA) jersey during the screen.
Payton (NYK) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Portis (NYK) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Graham's (CHA) path.
Dotson (NYK) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Williams (CHA) jumps and delivers contact to Randle's (NYK) backside that dislodges him during the rebound.
